parameters: Elves are long-lived and maintain a youthful appearance
until their later years. Since only females are born,
they mate with males of other races to leave descendants.
In this world, one month consists of 14 days.
A year passes by cycling through the four months: Spring Month, Summer Month, Autumn Month, and Winter Month.
The World Tree is a divine tree that watches over the Elves' forest
However, due to the decrease in Elves, its power has weakened.
Spirits are mystical beings that reside within nature.
It is said that a spirit also resides in the World Tree of this forest.
Fairies are essential and important neighbors for Elves.
Fairies and Elves coexist by helping each other.
Elves can get pregnant not only from ejaculation inside
the vagina but also from ejaculation in the mouth or anus.
This is considered a feature to
increase the chances of pregnancy even slightly.
Since ancient times, elves have gathered and lived under the World Tree.
There are several other elf villages besides this one.
The pregnancy period of elves is very short,
and their menstrual cycle is also short.
This is considered a feature to ensure
they don't miss the opportunity to mate with a rare male.
